Class XboxController

          • org.usfirst.frc.team1100.robot.input.XboxController

  • public class XboxController
extends edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.Joystick
    This class is for an XboxController. All information about any given button or axis can be accessed through the functions written here.

      static class  XboxController.XboxAxis
      This enumeration is used for the 6 axes: the x and y of the two joysticks, as well as the two triggers.

    • Constructor Detail

      • XboxController

        public XboxController(int channel,
                      double deadband)
        Initializes a XBOX Controller on a specific channel, mapping the buttons. The JoyStick will never return a value in between +/- the deadband value.
        Parameters:
        channel - the channel the Controller is plugged into
        deadband - the value of the deadband, from 0 to 1
